bt.data.range

Interface Range<T extends Range<T>>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DataRange
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BlockRange, ByteRange, DelegatingDataRange, SynchronizedDataRange, SynchronizedRange

    public interface Range<T extends Range<T>>
    Represents a range of binary data.
    Since:
    1.3
